text: Ghazi Mashal Ajil al-Yawar (, born 1958) is an Iraqi politician. He was the Vice President of Iraq from 2005 to 2006. He then served as President of Iraq from 2004 to 2005. ==References== Category:1958 births Category:Living people Category:Presidents of Iraq Category:Vice presidents of Iraq
title: Ghazi Mashal Ajil al-Yawer
